\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_7431896\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_7431896\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Sept 12, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104hha1720076228830.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hha1720076228830.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hha1720076228830.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"hxd1665702606673\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"hxd1665702606673__length_225134\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the number of characters in the specified string.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"hxd1665702606673__topic_d73751e1_d73752e1_d73753e1\">\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"hxd1665702606673__note_p1k_ftr_zbc\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> The <code class=\"ph codeph\">length</code> statement is deprecated. It has\n            been superseded by <code class=\"ph codeph\">$length</code> function, which is applicable to all\n            component types.</div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hxd1665702606673__p_d73754e1_d73755e1_d73756e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">length</span>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hxd1665702606673__p_d73757e1_d73758e1_d73759e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">length vString</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hxd1665702606673__topic_d48542e1_d48543e1_d48544e1_d48545e1_d48546e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d987509e83\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hxd1665702606673__p_d73763e1_d73764e1_d73765e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var>—string, or a field (or indirect reference to a field), a variable, or a function that evaluates to a string.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hxd1665702606673__topic_d48547e1_d48548e1_d48549e1_d48550e1_d48551e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d987509e95\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hxd1665702606673__p_d73769e1_d73770e1_d73771e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$result</span> is set to the number of characters in the string.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hxd1665702606673__p_d73772e1_d73773e1_d73774e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span> is not affected.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hxd1665702606673__topic_d48552e1_d48553e1_d48554e1_d48555e1_d48556e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d987509e113\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hxd1665702606673__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hxd1665702606673__topic_d48557e1_d48558e1_d48559e1_d48560e1_d48561e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d987509e123\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hxd1665702606673__p_d73784e1_d73785e1_d73786e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">length</span> statement finds the length of the piece of text in <var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var>. The value of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$result</span> is set to the number of characters in <var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var>.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hxd1665702606673__p_d73787e1_d73788e1_d73789e1\">If <var class=\"keyword varname\">String</var> contains frame marker, ruler, or character attribute characters, they are ignored.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"hxd1665702606673__p_d73790e1_d73791e1_d73792e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">length</span> statement is often used to determine where extraction should begin.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hxd1665702606673__section_jnm_ych_ybc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d987509e156\">Example: Find the Length of a String </h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following example finds the length of the string in vString:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"hxd1665702606673__pre_hn1_zch_ybc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">; store contents of NOTEPAD in vString\n; how long is string in vString?\n\nvString = \"test string\"\nlength vString\nvLength = $result\nOUTPUT = vLength\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"hxd1665702606673__section_og5_wch_ybc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d987509e168\">Example: Finding the Offset to Characters in a String </h2>\n<p class=\"p\">The following example uses the <code class=\"ph codeph\">length</code> statement to find\n            the offset to the last two characters in the string. In the example, the field INVNUM\n            contains the value 90021387SH. This is the concatenation of a date (13-Feb-1990), a\n            number (87), and a salesman's initials (SH):</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"hxd1665702606673__pre_kjf_xch_ybc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">; how long is invnum?\n; $1 contains position second from end\n; extract last 2 characters\n; report their total sales\n\nlength INVNUM\n$1=$result-1\n$2=INVNUM[$1]\nselectdb (sum(AMOUNT)) %/\n from \"INVOICES\" %/\n u_where (SALESCODE = $2) %/\n to SALESREPORT.DUMMY\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/toc1665703008287.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$length</a><p>Return the length of the specified argument.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bqr1665702555238.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$syntax</a><p>Convert a string to a syntax string.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ncx1686824523526.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$result</a><p>Return the result of certain ProcScript commands and tree widget events.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7431896\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7431896\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "length (deprecated) Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Sept 12, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Return the number of characters in the specified string. Note: The length statement is deprecated. It has been superseded by $length function, which is applicable to all component types. length String Example: length vString Parameters String —string, or a field (or indirect reference to a field), a variable, or a function that evaluates to a string. Return Values $result is set to the number of characters in the string. $status is not affected. Use Allowed in all component types. Description The length statement finds the length of the piece of text in String . The value of $result is set to the number of characters in String . If String contains frame marker, ruler, or character attribute characters, they are ignored. The length statement is often used to determine where extraction should begin. Example: Find the Length of a String The following example finds the length of the string in vString: ; store contents of NOTEPAD in vString ; how long is string in vString? vString = \"test string\" length vString vLength = $result OUTPUT = vLength Copy Example: Finding the Offset to Characters in a String The following example uses the length statement to find the offset to the last two characters in the string. In the example, the field INVNUM contains the value 90021387SH. This is the concatenation of a date (13-Feb-1990), a number (87), and a salesman's initials (SH): ; how long is invnum? ; $1 contains position second from end ; extract last 2 characters ; report their total sales length INVNUM $1=$result-1 $2=INVNUM[$1] selectdb (sum(AMOUNT)) %/ from \"INVOICES\" %/ u_where (SALESCODE = $2) %/ to SALESREPORT.DUMMY Copy Related Links $length Return the length of the specified argument. $syntax Convert a string to a syntax string. $result Return the result of certain ProcScript commands and tree widget events. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}